♪ <i>Some enchanted evening</i> ♪
♪ <i>Some enchanted evening</i> ♪

206
00:18:01,621 --> 00:18:06,585
♪ <i>When you find your true love</i> ♪

207
00:18:08,086 --> 00:18:11,631
